{"word":"καθαιρέω","slug":"καθαιρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰαϑαιρέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κατά\">κατά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:αἱρέω\">αἱρέω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘take down from a position’, <b>take down <a href='B:480 15:36'>Mk 15:36</a>, <a href='B:480 15:46'>46</a>; <a href='B:490 1:52'>Lk 1:52</a>; <a href='B:490 23:53'>23:53</a>; <a href='B:510 13:29'>Ac 13:29</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘destroy by taking down’, of structures <b>tear down <a href='B:490 12:18'>Lk 12:18</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> sense, of nations <b>destroy <a href='B:510 13:19'>Ac 13:19</a>;</b> in imagery, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <b>suffer loss</b> of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> <b><a href='B:510 19:27'>19:27</a>; demolish <a href='B:540 10:4'>2 Cor 10:4</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ s.\">s.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:καθαίρεσις\">καθαίρεσις</a></el>). <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:καθαίρεσις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:καθαίρω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}